1
00:00:58,202 --> 00:01:00,954
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,954 --> 00:01:02,938
=Episode 15=

3
00:01:03,418 --> 00:01:06,970
(No Grave to Mourn, Nowhere to Belong)

4
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:09,140
Master.

5
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,719
Speak freely.

6
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:22,079
As you instructed,
I've carefully examined that skeleton.

7
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:25,400
Based on the bone length and age,

8
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:29,159
it is most likely Master Zhaoxi.

9
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,840
Understood.

10
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:39,280
I think Chaosheng suspects
I stole that corpse,

11
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:42,560
so he sent people
to monitor our every move.

12
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,239
Do you need me to...?

13
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:44,920
No need.

14
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,719
If they want to watch us, let them.

15
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,400
But

16
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:53,000
if that corpse is truly Zhaoxi...

17
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,000
He died unjustly,

18
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:00,799
but I cannot mourn him.

19
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,280
Master.

20
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:08,680
But Chaosheng will likely act soon.

21
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:12,520
A corpse was found
beneath the wall of the Yunya Temple.

22
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:17,360
The pouch beside it
likely belongs to Chaosheng.

23
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:22,479
Investigate that corpse.

24
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,639
If my deduction is correct,

25
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:28,759
it must be...

26
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,759
(Physician Qin.)

27
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:38,080
The owner of Zuixian Building,
and Physician Qin.

28
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,280
These consecutive deaths

29
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,000
all happened just before we arrived.

30
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:45,039
They may not be coincidences.

31
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:48,599
You suspect a spy near your wife?

32
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:49,259
Tianlan.

33
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,080
Alright, I'll stop.

34
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,599
I'm just wondering who it might be.

35
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:59,199
Not that guard named Qing, is it?

36
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:03,199
I've scouted most
of this mansion by now.

37
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:06,240
Except for the old family head's room
and the tower atop the mountain.

38
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,800
I didn't dare approach carelessly.

39
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,400
What did you find?

40
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:18,159
Uneventful.

41
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:21,080
Gu Chaosheng appears
no different from a common merchant.

42
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,479
Gu Xuanji grows
many poisonous herbs in her courtyard.

43
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:29,120
She spends days studying them
or practicing dance at Zuixian Building.

44
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:32,639
As for Gu Wenshuang, he's simpler.

45
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:34,719
His room is barren.

46
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:37,960
He obsessively trains
in martial arts daily.

47
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,879
His skills are formidable.

48
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:43,120
I kept a distance to avoid alerting him.

49
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:48,080
Oh, about that drug
from Zuixian Building's owner,

50
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:51,159
you gave me the antidote,
but you inhaled it too.

51
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:53,199
How did you detoxify?

52
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,159
Keep watching that person.

53
00:03:57,639 --> 00:04:00,280
Gu Chaosheng has been monitoring
the Fufeng Pavilion.

54
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:02,879
Only contact me for urgent matters.

55
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:04,840
Yes.

56
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:23,600
Who's there?

57
00:04:41,850 --> 00:04:49,466
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

58
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,639
Why are you drinking?

59
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,879
Where are you going?

60
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,639
Xuanji invited me.

61
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:14,240
It's cold tonight. Sleep early.

62
00:06:09,114 --> 00:06:10,584
(Innocent yet hunted.
Circled by wolves, I can't mourn him.)

63
00:06:10,584 --> 00:06:11,519
(Peace? A dream. Where do I belong?)

64
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:13,360
(Why does fate toy with us?)

65
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:19,759
(When I learned
my own brother was still alive,)

66
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,360
(I received news of your death.)

67
00:06:24,079 --> 00:06:26,800
(When I thought I'd found love,)

68
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,920
(I discovered she was...)

69
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:35,319
(No grave to mourn, nowhere to belong.)

70
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:49,000
My presence prevents her
from mourning you.

71
00:07:03,706 --> 00:07:07,636
(Innocent yet hunted.
Circled by wolves, I can't mourn him.)

72
00:07:07,636 --> 00:07:10,394
(Peace? A dream. Where do I belong?)

73
00:07:10,778 --> 00:07:13,082
(Tomb of Tianji Lianyi)

74
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,620
Master.

75
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:26,079
I have nothing left to teach you.

76
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:28,959
You needn't call me Master.

77
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:34,160
Now, I'm merely a tomb keeper.

78
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,399
A teacher for a day
is a father for life.

79
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,920
Forget it. Your talent is extraordinary.

80
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,920
I've imparted all my knowledge to you.

81
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:50,199
The Tianji Sect has its successor.

82
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:54,480
But don't resent your father.

83
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:59,120
His position binds him inevitably.

84
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,120
How could I resent him?

85
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:07,399
How long since you genuinely smiled?

86
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:12,920
Lianyi perished with your brother
in that assassination.

87
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:19,639
Had he lived, you wouldn't be like this.

88
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,959
Though I blamed him
for Lianyi's death...

89
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:29,360
Your father made you Crown Prince
against all odds to protect you,

90
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:34,039
which endangered you instead.

91
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:40,639
So he feigned neglect to protect you.

92
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,960
Why this new grave?

93
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:54,440
In our sect, spouses
share life and death.

94
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:59,480
Who knows how many years
I have left as a tomb keeper?

95
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,360
Master.

96
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:05,879
You should leave.

97
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:10,279
In life, what is true or false?

98
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:15,919
Truth and illusion intertwine.

99
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,559
Only when you dare
to believe can you truly see.

100
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:23,279
Don't wait until regret consumes you.

101
00:09:25,690 --> 00:09:29,082
(Yin Ci's Tomb)

102
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:39,559
(The face remains unknown,
yet my heart is bound.)

103
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:45,759
(Together in life
beneath the Milky Way.)

104
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:51,799
(Separated but still longing
for the reunion.)

105
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:58,000
(Pursuing shadows in recurrent dreams.)

106
00:10:00,279 --> 00:10:05,039
(Divided by a cruel destiny
to the ends of the earth.)

107
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:11,039
(But our brotherly love
shines across the world.)

108
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:19,039
(Where in the underworld
will I find my brother?)

109
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:28,480
(Tears accompany the twinkling stars.)

110
00:10:58,639 --> 00:11:01,879
What brings you here today, Yuluo?

111
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:05,960
You've been asking me
to meet up for days, haven't you?

112
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:09,759
But why are you at this tea house?

113
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:11,019
Yes.

114
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:14,399
I've been planning a reopening ceremony
for Zuixian Building,

115
00:11:14,799 --> 00:11:16,799
where I'll also announce
the handover then.

116
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:20,639
Wanting to know my competition,
I came to visit this nearby shop first.

117
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,200
Could you help me with this?

118
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:30,279
I plan to perform a dance that day.
Could you offer some guidance?

119
00:11:31,799 --> 00:11:34,879
I'm not that good. I'm no match for you.

120
00:11:35,639 --> 00:11:39,639
Who says that? Your dance
in Suzhou captivated everyone.

121
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:42,279
I wonder if I'm lucky enough
to watch it today.

122
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:47,840
Even small matters in such a tiny place
like Suzhou don't escape your notice.

123
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:50,679
You always surprise me.

124
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,600
I just happened to pass by.

125
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:55,279
I noticed that tavern was lively,
so I took a look.

126
00:11:56,039 --> 00:12:00,720
But General Shen happened
to be there too. What a coincidence.

127
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:08,519
You're still worrying about me?

128
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,720
Why not worry about yourself?

129
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:11,820
Me?

130
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,440
Why?

131
00:12:14,919 --> 00:12:18,159
You're worried that my clumsy dance
might embarrass me in public?

132
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,960
Your dance is, of course, graceful.

133
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:24,919
But the sudden change of ownership
at Zuixian Building is rather strange.

134
00:12:25,799 --> 00:12:28,120
The former owner met an unusual death.

135
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:30,480
Her death has nothing to do with me.

136
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:32,320
This is a legitimate transaction.

137
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:34,159
Of course.

138
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:38,440
But the family ship is already rocking.

139
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:41,879
And you want to throw
a big ceremony right now.

140
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:44,600
If you're fishing for someone,

141
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,120
our meeting today
is already more than enough.

142
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,120
I'll keep that in mind.

143
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:55,000
Though I'm surprised
that you'd tell me this.

144
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:58,960
Didn't you also give me a generous gift?

145
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,679
I don't have any great gift.

146
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:04,559
If there's anything here
that you find desirable,

147
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:05,960
you can take it freely.

148
00:13:07,559 --> 00:13:10,039
Is a dagger given to someone
a sincere gift of protection

149
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:12,360
or a hidden scheme?

150
00:13:13,639 --> 00:13:16,480
It depends on who's using it.

151
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:20,519
Are you referring to you
as the person using it?

152
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,399
Or me?

153
00:13:24,799 --> 00:13:27,919
What do you think is the difference
between an assassin and a spy?

154
00:13:31,399 --> 00:13:34,000
An assassin needs weapons.
A spy does not.

155
00:13:34,799 --> 00:13:37,320
Weapons would expose a spy's identity.

156
00:13:38,039 --> 00:13:39,200
For a spy,

157
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:42,759
everything in the world,
even an opponent's weapon,

158
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,159
can be used.

159
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:52,200
It's late. I'll be leaving now.

160
00:14:19,519 --> 00:14:22,559
(Between you and me, is it sincerity)

161
00:14:23,399 --> 00:14:25,039
(or a hidden scheme?)

162
00:15:17,399 --> 00:15:18,200
Master.

163
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:27,399
Few people know this poem.

164
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,840
It was left by a poet from the past

165
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:32,399
for an old friend.

166
00:15:33,759 --> 00:15:36,000
Not a word of death
or parting is spoken,

167
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:39,039
yet each line is about vast landscapes,

168
00:15:39,399 --> 00:15:40,559
fine wine,

169
00:15:41,759 --> 00:15:43,279
and a lonely yearning.

170
00:15:46,279 --> 00:15:47,639
That's so thoughtful of you.

171
00:16:08,639 --> 00:16:10,399
Has Master Chaosheng sent anyone here?

172
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,039
No.

173
00:16:14,399 --> 00:16:16,600
He's more patient than I expected.

174
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:20,840
As you instructed days ago,
I've been secretly following him.

175
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:24,679
Refused by the family head,
he secretly went to the Xuanji Pavilion.

176
00:16:25,159 --> 00:16:27,320
But Gu Xuanwu also...

177
00:16:28,759 --> 00:16:32,559
You were sure he'd come today
because the authorities

178
00:16:32,919 --> 00:16:35,000
are about to trace
the pouch back to him?

179
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:38,240
If he's going to use
the Xuanji Pavilion...

180
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:40,799
Today, I had a conversation with Xuanji.

181
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,399
She intentionally mentioned

182
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:46,639
that she once saw me dancing
for General Shen in Suzhou.

183
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:50,919
That task was carried out in secrecy.

184
00:16:53,679 --> 00:16:55,519
Only you and I know of it.

185
00:16:57,039 --> 00:16:59,039
Master, Heaven tasks
are highly confidential.

186
00:16:59,039 --> 00:17:02,440
I absolutely won't mention it to anyone
or do anything to leak information.

187
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:09,279
Stand up. I surely trust you.

188
00:17:35,519 --> 00:17:38,880
A few days ago, assassins sneaked
into the Fufeng Pavilion.

189
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:42,640
You were ambushed and fell unconscious.
While dealing with the assassins,

190
00:17:43,319 --> 00:17:44,119
you said,

191
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,839
you heard something unusual.

192
00:17:48,079 --> 00:17:51,200
Yes, at that time, my mind was muddled.

193
00:17:51,799 --> 00:17:54,640
But during the fight,
I seemed to hear something unusual.

194
00:17:55,039 --> 00:17:58,839
It was as if someone
was secretly helping.

195
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:01,759
Understood.

196
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:10,119
Young Madam, officials from the yamen
are here about the missing body.

197
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:12,880
Master Chaosheng needs you
to go over and answer some questions.

198
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:23,759
Understood.

199
00:18:40,599 --> 00:18:43,119
You stay here. I'll be back soon.

200
00:19:07,799 --> 00:19:08,720
Do you know your crime?

201
00:19:12,079 --> 00:19:14,079
That depends on
what you're accusing me of.

202
00:19:15,359 --> 00:19:18,480
Where's that unclaimed body
from the yamen now?

203
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:22,160
Since no one claimed it,
how would I know?

204
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:25,559
Let me put it another way.

205
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:29,039
Where was your guard today?

206
00:19:30,119 --> 00:19:30,920
Today?

207
00:19:32,559 --> 00:19:34,200
The pharmacy received new herbs,

208
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:36,359
so I sent her to take inventory.

209
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:38,240
If you feel unwell,

210
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:42,839
I can have her bring
some tonics to you tomorrow.

211
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:45,720
Inventory?

212
00:20:12,839 --> 00:20:13,680
What happened?

213
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:14,759
Where's Yuluo?

214
00:20:15,359 --> 00:20:17,759
Taken away by Master Chaosheng's man.
He doesn't mean well.

215
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:19,920
It might be related to Master Zhaoxi.

216
00:20:55,834 --> 00:21:00,897
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

217
00:21:01,434 --> 00:21:06,755
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

218
00:21:07,322 --> 00:21:13,950
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

219
00:21:13,950 --> 00:21:18,714
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

220
00:21:18,714 --> 00:21:21,050
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

221
00:21:21,050 --> 00:21:27,750
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

222
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:34,522
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

223
00:21:34,522 --> 00:21:41,658
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

224
00:21:41,658 --> 00:21:46,042
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

225
00:21:46,042 --> 00:21:48,666
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

226
00:21:48,666 --> 00:21:55,300
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

227
00:21:55,300 --> 00:22:01,850
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

228
00:22:01,850 --> 00:22:08,974
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

229
00:22:09,064 --> 00:22:13,434
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

230
00:22:13,434 --> 00:22:16,142
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

231
00:22:16,142 --> 00:22:22,042
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

232
00:22:22,682 --> 00:22:28,670
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
